Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.97,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I don't wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:36.26,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:39.00,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Reason as against emotion 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:43.93,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I've gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:47.15,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}All my effort will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:50.30,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Endless desire,like a haunting refrairn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:53.56,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Such a pain ,the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:56.14,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}There is a way to change the word
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:57.77,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:01:00.97,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}So what if sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:03.14,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:07.84,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.43,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:12.74,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}"A Whole New World God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.72,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I'll always be on your side  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.96,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I know you're hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:20.22,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}To be a knight    To be a light   For you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:20.34,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:21.89,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}No more fears      No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:23.27,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Everything will work out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:25.38,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}That's "God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:27.64,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.36,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}This is not real love 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:32.84,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}But I'll do anying for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.69,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Whatever happens in my self,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:38.67,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Remember,no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:38.84,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Every and leads to a new beginning of the next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:41.66,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Try to make my life complete ,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:44.17,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:48.94,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Don't look back,carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:51.77,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Be your self...Be happy...It's your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.24,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}"God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:56.60,OP_en,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Find your love...Find your way...For your life...
